{"fadeType":1,"once":true,"scripts":[{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"paingtingGray":true,"say":"“They're wrapping around us! Hold them off at all costs!”","dir":1,"actorName":"？？？","bgm":"battle-boss-4","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"nameColor":"#a9f548","effects":[{"active":true,"name":"memoryFog"}],"actor":303110,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"dialogShake":{"x":8.5,"number":2,"speed":0.09},"say":"There was something odd about her recollections.","soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Their bodies were different. Their thoughts and their actions and their movements were different. They looked like humans, but they could not be further from the wisdom of humanity.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Takao, let's retreat! We've been totally routed!","dir":1,"actorName":"？？？","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"paingtingGray":true,"actor":302130,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Hold on a little longer! Reinforcements will arrive soon!","dir":1,"actorName":"？？？","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"paingtingGray":true,"actor":303110,"blackBg":true},{"side":2,"dialogShake":{"x":8.5,"number":2,"speed":0.09},"say":"Even the strongest weapon, without the \"guidance\" and \"wisdom\" of mankind, would be nothing more than a tool of indiscriminate destruction.","soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"paingtingGray":true,"say":"Faced with the might of advanced weaponry as well as the violent forces of nature, the helpless girls could do nothing but retreat.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"What's what over there?! Some kind of wall?!","dir":1,"actorName":"？？？","side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":30,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"paingtingGray":true,"actor":301140,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Hold on!","dir":1,"actorName":"？？？","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"paingtingGray":true,"actor":303110,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Th-this is...","dir":1,"actorName":"？？？","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"paingtingGray":true,"actor":303110,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Is this... Watatsumi...?!","dir":1,"actorName":"？？？","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"paingtingGray":true,"actor":303110,"blackBg":true},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"...","dir":1,"actorName":"？？？","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"effects":[{"active":false,"name":"memoryFog"}],"actor":900192,"stopbgm":true,"flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Accursed Sirens...!","dir":1,"actorName":"？？？","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900192,"blackBg":true},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"Diadem of Light - Ceremonial Hall","dir":1,"bgm":"main-newyear","side":2,"bgmDelay":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Watatsumi, one of the sacred artifacts of the Sakura Empire, was brought out before one of the ceremonial halls.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"On the surface, there was nothing about this stone's appearance that appeared \"sacred.\" It was a simple stone, navy-blue in color.","dir":1,"effects":[{"active":true,"name":"juqingshitou"}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Faintly it glowed, bathed in the light of the moon pouring through the window.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Then, the silence was broken...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true},{"expression":8,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Now then, this ceremony shall now commence upon Akagi's orders on behalf of Ryuuhou, who is unable to join us tonight.","actor":301100,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"effects":[{"active":false,"name":"juqingshitou"}],"blackBg":true,"dir":1},{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"This is just a rehearsal, Yamashiro! Come on, you're up!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"actor":301100,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"W-woah... this is the sacred artifact said to harbor the power of a sea god? Hmm, looks rather ordinary though...","actor":305020,"blackBg":true,"dir":1,"side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Um, everyone, please watch me conduct the ritual!","actor":305020,"blackBg":true,"dir":1,"side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"\"Lift your voices in praise of Watatsumi. Show your courage, and admire its wisdom.\"","dir":1,"actorName":"Everyone","side":2,"effects":[{"active":true,"name":"juqingshitou"}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"\"Sing its praises so that it may guide us to the path of light.\"","dir":1,"blackBg":true,"actorName":"Everyone","side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"\"May our lands be forever blessed to stave away calamity.\"","dir":1,"blackBg":true,"actorName":"Everyone","side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"ZAP!!","dir":1,"flashN":{"alpha":[[0,1,0.2],[1,0,0.2,0.2]],"color":[1,1,1]},"side":2,"soundeffect":"event:\/ui\/kuang","stopbgm":true,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"As Yamashiro reached out to touch Watatsumi, she was repelled, as if pushed away by an unseen force.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true},{"expression":5,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"H-huh?","actor":301100,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"effects":[{"active":false,"name":"juqingshitou"}],"blackBg":true,"dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Cease this ceremony this instant! Step away from that stone!","dir":1,"bgm":"story-7","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"action":[{"type":"shake","y":30,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"actor":305050},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Nagato and Zuikaku rushed into the hall.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Nagato! You're safe!","actor":305110,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"*tsk*...","actor":307010,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"That stone is enchanted to repel everything except for those from the Sakura Empire! What are you?!","actor":305050,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Following Nagato's lead, the other ships at the hall sprung to their feet.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Eh? Ehhhhhh?","actor":305020,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"As if reality itself was peeling away, a figure - neither Iron Blood nor Sakura Empire - stepped forward from behind Yamashiro.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"I was pretty confident about my disguise too. How unfortunate that it was seen through so easily~","actor":900012,"dir":1,"actorName":"Observer","side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Siren!!","dir":1,"actorName":"Everyone","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Did you sneak in like this? How cowardly!","actor":307060,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Oh my, looks like my forces couldn't finish the job out there?","actor":900012,"dir":1,"actorName":"Observer","side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"What a pity... if that \"Ember\" girl hadn't gotten in my way, none of you would even be here right now.","actor":900012,"dir":1,"actorName":"Observer","side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"What do you plan to do with Watatsumi?!","actor":305050,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Hehehe, who knows...","actor":900012,"dir":1,"actorName":"Observer","side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Lady Nagato, watch out...!","actor":301490,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Before Observer had a chance to move, the roof of the ceremonial hall was ripped open by an explosion.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"flashN":{"alpha":[[0,1,0.2],[1,0,0.2,0.2],[0,1,0.2,0.4],[1,0,0.2,0.6]],"color":[1,1,1]},"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Under the force of the blast, the wood and concrete of the ceiling sheared away, leaving the hall half-open.","dir":1,"effects":[{"active":true,"name":"miwu_01"}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Fortunately, nobody was injured by falling debris.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I knew you'd come, \"Ember.\" Hehehe... See, I knew there was a lot for us to talk about.","dir":1,"actorName":"Observer","side":2,"action":[{"type":"move","y":-1250,"delay":1,"dur":0.5,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"As quickly as she entered, Observer seemed to melt into the environment and disappeared.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Showing up and disappearing like ghosts... are there any other Sirens?","actor":305110,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Despite the sense of panic, everyone at the scene scanned their surroundings, preparing for further threats.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"expression":5,"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"I'm sorry, Mikasa. I let an enemy slip through the line...","dir":1,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"actor":301810,"side":2},{"expression":5,"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Sorry... I didn't do my job...","dir":1,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"actor":301810,"side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Don't worry about it. Keep maintaining your guard around the island. Even if the elite Sirens are able to slip through, at least the mass-produced models won't be able to get through.","actor":305110,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"(That \"Ember\" person that she mentioned... was she the one who attacked us...?)","actor":305110,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":6,"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Um, excuse me! What should Hibiki do...?","dir":1,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"actor":301100,"side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Stay here and protect Nagato and Watatsumi. Shoukaku and I will go intercept the attacking enemies!","actor":307060,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Leave it to me!","actor":305110,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"FUYINGYINGHUA22","fadeOut":1.5}